{"tid":729601,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★海外完成課程後回港生活 90後墮樓爆頭亡","createTime":"2018-07-04T16:43:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-11T00:48:19.000Z","uid":19454,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"b810bec0ee4d9819b001a0bb83f25efa175035b7","tid":729601,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T16:43:21.000Z","msg":"沙田第一城男子墮樓亡。今晚（4日）8時23分，有途人行經沙田第一城第22座時，乍聞一聲砰然巨響，見一名男子倒臥地上浴血昏迷，途人隨即報警求助。警員及救護員接報到場，經初步檢查後，證實男子頭爆肢折，當場死亡。<br />\n<br />\n警方封鎖現場，並用帳篷遮蓋遺體，現場沒有檢獲遺書。消息指，死者26歲姓黃，早前從海外完成課程後<span style=\"color: red;\">回港生活</span>，與母親居於上址一個單位。據悉，他有情緒病紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180704/bkn-20180704222051968-0704_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180704%2Fbkn-20180704222051968-0704_00822_001.html&d=QI3%2Bix5GhDl9L2D%2BKypL%2FARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=734eee4f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180704/bkn-20180704222051968-0704_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"df7a80ed4e017681f411ff9d182688124e418fe0","tid":729601,"uid":19454,"like":63,"dislike":1,"score":62,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T16:43:47.000Z","msg":"回港生活=jump into hell"},{"pid":"b535a1949346666d3c652b5b310b7b3fbaecee59","tid":729601,"uid":29929,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T16:47:21.000Z","msg":"高登腦魔真係你黎？<br />\n<br />\n膠力差左咁多既"},{"pid":"a898a746b78e3a4d925e0fd5160680bb8318f1ea","tid":729601,"uid":70964,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T16:48:32.000Z","msg":"情緒病害死人"},{"pid":"2890c3abb85a1313fff6fb637cb65a292e4661ba","tid":729601,"uid":127988,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T16:48:52.000Z","msg":"恭喜自殺成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a3a1c6f8399195308f16b0f19168de14efdc5ac","tid":729601,"uid":86418,"like":2,